{
  "stem": "24515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told later that while I was absent at one time, he-- so would always beg the class.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He couldn't-- you know, couldn't be the Jew were the only one who knew the history.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would they please do something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I don't know if this is terribly anti-Semitic, but it's, I suppose, indicative of what's going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I say, in the school, the-- the faculty and the administration, if anything, protected us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried to be as fair and as decent-- it wasn't for a long while we were there, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until at the end of-- toward the end of '38, before Kristallnacht, the headmaster, the director-- the [NON-ENGLISH] director called us to his office.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with clearly embarrassment and regret, told us that we couldn't attend any longer, that there was a law out now that-- to-- to stop us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to-- well, my parents sent me to Berlin, to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not quite as humanistic as the Humanistic Gymnasium, but it's still along those lines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, this man, I'm quite certain, was not meant to [? seem ?] [? mad. ?] And I think he was sorry to have to do this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the other hand, he also didn't resign or something, or say-- or say, to heck with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very, very few did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When-- you know, you've heard this said, I think, that until the final solution got into action-- you know, the-- the thing that Spielberg wrote about-- showed the movie about, and the-- the other movie about the Shoah and so on.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until that happened, was a very salami activity, a piece of-- slice of salami.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One thing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then another thing happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then another thing happened, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
